Zone comment: 0.61-0.75 Ma based on the co-occurrence of G. tosaensis and G. hessi.
Comment (general): Frosty. A count was made out of 310 specimens. This sample mostly consisted of glass shards. Mainly foraminifera in the >150um fraction but not many.

Comment (general): Possible reworking. Presence of G. acostaensis and G. limbata. Abundance data based on 1/4 split.

Datum comment: 1.93-1.64 Ma based on the co-occurrence of G. apertura and G. truncatulinoides. Also G. multicamerata (several very nice specimens). Photographed but not included in age range as possibly reworked and G. truncatulinoides is much more abundant (gives upper age limit incompatible with presence of G. multicamerata).
